00:00:24.040 --> 00:00:27.970
Let me recall that the
derivative of a function, if it

00:00:27.970 --> 00:00:34.790
exists, which we denote
by f prime of c, this

00:00:34.790 --> 00:00:39.530
is the limit as x
goes to c of f of x

00:00:39.530 --> 00:00:45.260
minus f of c over x minus c.

00:00:45.260 --> 00:00:51.500
Last time, we looked at the
relationship between continuity

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:56.290
