00:01:03.880 --> 00:01:05.920
Because there are
continuous functions,

00:01:05.920 --> 00:01:08.050
which we actually constructed.

00:01:08.050 --> 00:01:09.910
We constructed a
continuous function.

00:01:09.910 --> 00:01:11.500
You can generalize that example.

00:01:15.010 --> 00:01:17.070
So we constructed a
continuous function

00:01:17.070 --> 00:01:20.230
that is differentiable nowhere.

00:01:20.230 --> 00:01:25.440
So in fact, differentiability
is a much stronger condition

00:01:25.440 --> 00:01:26.370
than continuity.

00:01:26.370 --> 00:01:27.885
And it's something of a miracle.

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:39.200
Just as a side note, if you go
on to study complex analysis,

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:41.170
